description:
A
 big pallete with 7 colors and 9 shades, equalling a total of 63 colors.
 I made this pallete for a RPG game where color diversity was a must, so
 it is great for many things. The pallete is inspired by AdamCYounis, 
that's why the base colors are the same as Apollo. Hope you like it. :)
